author: Joe Scott
description:
To try everything Brilliant has to offer for free, visit http://brilliant.org/answerswithjoe. You’ll also get 20% off an annual premium subscription!

Today’s compilation gets into some tragic events and places in history. So prepare for a couple hours of death and disaster - just the perfect thing for Thanksgiving!

This compilation includes:
